# Marathon bundle 9 (4c) — ephemeral Playwright video output.
# Walkthrough captures land here as webm; the encode script reads
# them and writes mp4/gif assets under docs-site/static/img/walkthroughs/.
# The webm files are not committed (they are ~3-5x larger than the
# mp4 + gif combined and have no consumer outside this script).
.output/
